{"tid":95594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"流亡日本漫畫家「變態辣椒」新作《中國共產黨撒謊》　登當地暢銷榜","createTime":"2017-01-26T07:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T08:04:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e10da85d07c96289de198fb3293bfcb4ab9c3998","tid":95594,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"漫畫家「變態辣椒」王立銘因作品內容諷刺北京，在2014年遭大陸官媒大力抨擊，現時已流亡日本。他近日於日本推出漫畫書，書名日文直譯為《中國共產黨撒謊》，繼續以漫畫批判中共，新書已登上多個暢銷排行榜。<br />\n<br />\n據《美國之音》報道，變態辣椒的新書在1月18日已在日本發行。該書目前在日本亞馬遜網購排行榜上，於「中國問題書籍類」排名第一位。負責出版《中國共產黨撒謊》的編輯三邊直太透露，該書發行6天後第一版六千本已近售罄，出版商決定增印1萬本，估計今後還會繼續增印。<br />\n<br />\n該漫畫另設中文版，名為《變態辣椒&mdash;流亡中的漫畫家》，於亞馬遜的書籍簡介寫有「流亡漫畫家冒死描繪獨裁國家的真相」；「中國的政治警察有哪些超乎想象的惡毒手段？」；「F*ck you, Xi JinPing!」等字眼。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n報道指，新書用很大篇幅描述中共反日教育如何滲透國民意識，並舉例指北京一所著名公立小學教學生「照」字口訣：「一個日本人、拿著一把刀、殺了一口人、流下四滴血。」<br />\n<br />\n變態辣椒曾就溫州動車事故、艾未未案、習近平新政乃至本港普選爭議等政治議題作諷刺畫作，2013年他轉發一條災區微博，隨即被警以「涉嫌尋釁滋事」傳喚。2014年他在遊日期間，遭大陸官媒《人民網》點名批評為漢奸，他於是決定流亡日本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C2ImkeOVEAA3KSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC2ImkeOVEAA3KSL.jpg&h=e77f9929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6-%E8%AE%8A%E6%85%8B%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92-%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E6%92%92%E8%AC%8A-%E7%99%BB%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E6%9A%A2%E9%8A%B7%E6%A6%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2585%258B%25E8%25BE%25A3%25E6%25A4%2592-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E6%2592%2592%25E8%25AC%258A-%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%259A%25A2%25E9%258A%25B7%25E6%25A6%259C%2F&d=VEnvoTX589ayptzzh3AaWQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8e6e4fb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2585%258B%25E8%25BE%25A3%25E6%25A4%2592-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%259C-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E6%2592%2592%25E8%25AC%258A-%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%259A%25A2%25E9%258A%25B7%25E6%25A6%259C%2F&h=db17729f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6-%E8%AE%8A%E6%85%8B%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92-%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E6%92%92%E8%AC%8A-%E7%99%BB%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E6%9A%A2%E9%8A%B7%E6%A6%9C/</a>"},{"pid":"691e735f4a4d35c421189274a8e3740d87387173","tid":95594,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"正評是我給的"},{"pid":"a43e6287b31e20957e18276066df58441e14823c","tid":95594,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"唔怪得689....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎想升職加人mm"},{"pid":"7747a96f1c4bb9bfc8663091a7d90f0bd52cb03e","tid":95594,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怪得689....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎想升職加人工</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d18031ef9c6af6da5a8dc48278003cd38a91ab3e","tid":95594,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}